OL,3,CInquest into the death of former
OL,4,CEngland cricketer Graham Thorpe opens
OL,6,FFormer England batter Graham Thorpe
OL,7,Fdied after being struck by a train at
OL,8,Fa railway station in Surrey, the
OL,9,Fopening of an inquest into his death
OL,10,Fhas heard.
OL,12,FThe 55-year-old took his own life, his
OL,13,Fwife Amanda revealed on Monday in an
OL,14,Finterview with The Times.
OL,16,FIn the same interview, Thorpe's
OL,17,Fdaughter Kitty said the family "are
OL,18,Fnot ashamed" of talking about his
OL,19,Fdeath, adding: "There is nothing to
OL,20,Fhide and it is not a stigma."
