OL,6,FThe area coroner for Surrey, Simon
OL,7,FWickens, recorded the former
OL,8,Fcricketer's cause of death as one of
OL,9,Fmultiple injuries during the short
OL,10,Fhearing.
OL,12,FThe coroner offered his "sincere
OL,13,Fcondolences" not just to Thorpe's
OL,14,Ffamily, but to "all those touched by
OL,15,Fhis life and career".
OL,17,FA date for the full inquest will be
OL,18,Ffixed at a later time.
