OL,6,FJulie Bentley added: "Talking openly
OL,7,Fcan help to break the stigma
OL,8,Fsurrounding the subject and can
OL,9,Fencourage people who are struggling to
OL,10,Fget the vital support they need."
OL,12,FThorpe was a mainstay in the England
OL,13,Fset-up for many years, first as a
OL,14,Fbatter between 1993 and 2005 before he
OL,15,Fspent 12 years in coaching roles, but
OL,16,Fwas admitted to hospital in May 2022
OL,17,Fand declared "seriously ill".
