OL,6,FDuring a distinguished international
OL,7,Fcareer, he struck 16 Test hundreds for
OL,8,FEngland, including a debut century
OL,9,Fagainst Australia at Trent Bridge in
OL,10,F1993, and represented his country 182
OL,11,Ftimes in all formats.
OL,13,FCurrent Test players Ben Stokes, Joe
OL,14,FRoot and Ben Duckett hailed Thorpe
OL,15,Fafter the news of his death emerged,
OL,16,Fwhile retired England bowler Stuart
OL,17,FBroad described him as a "wonderful
OL,18,Fperson".
